summary: Profiling Marvel's Power Pack of Superkids
title: Profiling Marvel's Power Pack of Superkids
body:
Profiling Marvel’s Power Pack of Superkids

Four kids fight crime with the best of ’em in Marvel’s fictional universe, and they’re called the Power Pack.

First appearing way back in 1984, the Power Pack put their youthful stamp on stomping out crime for over 60 issues.

“Power Pack is the first team of preteen superheroes in the Marvel Universe and the first in comics to operate without adult supervision.”

Super kids sans adult…

caption:
I love Halloween, so here is 2018′s masterlist of Halloween themed one-shots that will be posted.

Feel free to send in requests up until the 31st!

Join my tag list here

Check out 2017′s masterlist here.

Scream Queens [bestfriend!Harrison Osterfield x Fem!Reader]

Summary: It was a tradition to watch a horror film on Halloween night, unfortunately you thought your best friends were men instead of scream queens but this Halloween ends up with a bittersweet twist.

Friday Fright Night [Boyfriend!Peter Parker x Fem!Reader]

Summary: When a Haunted House freaks the pair of you out more than expected.

Undress [Boyfriend!Tom Holland x Fem!Reader]

Summary: It’s not every day you get to dress up as your boyfriend.

Upside Down Romance [Peter Parker x Fem!Reader]

Summary: You work up the courage to ask Peter if he’s ever tried the iconic Spiderman kiss
